channel.desc: PREMIERE: When young Minna discovers a portal into the world of dreams?where blue creatures called Dreambuilders craft other people?s fantasies?she starts tinkering with her step-sister Jenny?s dreams. But meddling has consequences: Jenny falls into a coma and Minna must brave the dream realm's dangers to save her.
